@rklos

> I cannot click on any Google link, even after disabling all filters and extensions. When I try to click a google result, I get the error "Unsafe JavaScript attempt to initiate navigation for frame with URL" in the browser console.

Hi. Please write to support@adguard.com or to https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardForMac/issues
